reviews.review_text: Thanks! The tape is rough in spots, but this is a terrific show. Thanks for transferring and uploading this.

phil lesh plays the electric bass guitar  with astounding color and imagination through the second set.  eyes of the world - they're having too much fun and can't bring themselves to stop.

so what about the sound quality - i'm too mesmerized by the grooves to bother nitpicking about it.  it's a shitty washed out nth generation tape.  but who cares.  wicked show.
